# AutoSpace

## Document:
System Requirement Specification Document

## Title:
System Reqruiement Spefication for AutoSpace (online vehicle service booking system)

## Team: 
Direct Customer,Indirect Customer,Architect,Business Analyst,Quality Assurance Team, System Analyst

## Objective (Purpose):
The AutoSpace Web Applictaion is intended to  provide complete solution for Consumers as well as internal users (Staff) through  a single Gateway using internet. 
It will enable customers to browse through virtual service center and book a servicing slot for car without visting a center.

## Scope:
The ability for customers to select the type of service they require along with date and time they would like the appointment to take place.
The ability for customers to make payments for their service booking online. 
Customer will be able to  review booking history and may able to cancel booking within 24 hours of order place.
The System  will be able to show live Bussion Operation statistics trends through Customized dashboard for stakeholders.

## Definitions:
	OVSBS: Online Vehicle Service Booking System
	QA:  Quality Assurance
	Portal: Peronalized Online Web Application
	MIS: Management Information System
	CRM: Customer Relation Managment
	BI:  Business Intelligence
	KPI:Key Perfomornace 
	Dashboard: Personalized information presented using  BI techniques such grid, score card, graph, KPI


## Functional Requirements:

Any annonymous User will be able to view different services avaialble on website.
Registered Customer will be able to select different packages for thier vehicle servicing and repair.
Center Manager will be able to approve or reject request for servicing slot booked by customer.
Center Manager will able to track and maintain slots available of servicing.
Customer will be able request to add new specific requirement maintained by system.
Customer will be able to update vehicle details which have been already added to vehicle list.
Customer will be able to update his/ her personal information. 
service packages will be provided based their category, sale, quantity, likes, recommendations.
Consumer will be able to  add or remove service packages and additional requirements from cart. System will maintain cart for each consumer to maintain list of services selected by him/her. Consumer will be able view all services from cart. Cart will present package details, number of packages and  additional services  selected by consumer with price and total. Consumer will be able process for Order placement.
Registered Customer will be able place an order with the help of cart maintained by system. Registered Customer will be able to cancel placed order within 24 hours. Registered customer get orders history. Registered customer can get details of order from orderes been placed. 	
Admin will be able to see summary of orders been placed , rejected from Orders Processing of System. Admin will get Business insight by observing  daily operations  with the of getting orders information.
Consumer will be provided options for payment such as through internet banking  or  UPI  or Online payment option.
Consumer will asked to submit their payment related information.Consumer will be redirected to payment gateway for secure payment transaction.On successfull payment processing using payment gateway system will notify consumer about transaction and order placement status.
Customer will be able track servicing status.
pickup/drop person will be able get pickup/drop details so that he / she can pickup/drop vehicle to customer end.
Delivery person will be able to change the status of vehicle delivered.
Center Manager will be able to list all vehicle deliveries to be done by their staff.
Customer will able to submit feedback about service they recieved.
Customer will be notified about order status, delivery status through  SMS/Email communication.
Customer will get complete information about his orders, details through a dashboard.
Customer will be able to update his payment related information.
System will present dashboard for Customers, Center Manager,Pickup/Drop person,Admin.
Dashboard will provide information using graph, score cards, key perfomance indicators as well Grid data prestation.
	
## NonFunctional Requirement:

### Security
Registered Customer will allowed to place an order.	
Each stakeholder will be to access system  through authentication process. Who are you ?
System will provide access to  the content , operations using Role based security (Authorization) (Permissions based on Role)
Using SSL in all transactions  which will be performed stakeholder. It would protect confidential information shared by system to stake holder of Shared by stakeholder to system.
System will automatically log of  all stakeholder after some time due to inactiveness.
System will block operations for inactive  stakeholder and would redirect for authentication.
System  will internally maintain secure communiction channel between Servers ( Web Servers, App Servers, databse Server)
Sensitive data will be always encrypted across communcation.
User proper firewall to protect servers from out side fishing, velnerable attacks.


### Reliability
The system will backup business data on regular basis and recover in short time duration to keep system operational
Continous updates are matained , continous Adminstration is done to keep system operational.
During peak hours system will maintain same user experaince by managing load balacning .

### Availability
uptime:   24* 7  available  99.999%
	
### Maintainability:
A Commercial database software will be used to maintain System data Persistence.
IT operations team will easily monitor and configure System using Adminstrative tools provided by Servers.
Separate enviornment will be maintained for system for isolation in  production, testing, and development.

### Portablility:
PDA: Portable Device Application
System will provide portable User Interface ( HTML, CSS, JS) through  users will be able to access AutoSpace portal.
System can be deployed to single server, multi server, to any OS, Cloud (Azure or AWS or GCP)

### Accessibility:
only registered customer will be able to place an order after authentication.
Center Manager can reject or approve customer order and  additional requests.
BOD team will be able to view daily, weekly, monthly, annual businss Growth throgh customized dashboard.S

### Durability:
System will retain customer cart for 15 minutes  even though customer loose internet connection and join again.
System will implement backup and recovery for retaining stake holders data, bussiness operation data and business data over time.

### Efficiency:
maximum number of users will place order, view products  with same response time.
System will be able to manage all transactions with isolation.

### Modularity:
System will designed and developed using reusable, independent or dependent business senarios in the form of modules.
These modules will be loosely coupled and highly cohesive.
System will contain CRM,cart, order processing, payment processing, Delivery module,Roles managment modules.
	
### Scalability:
System will be able  to  provide  consistent user exeprience to stake holder as well as vistors irrespective of load.

### Safety:	
online shopping portal will be secure from malicious attack, fishing.
online shoppping portal functionalilites are protected from outside with prper firewall configuration.
online shopping portal will be always kept updated with latest anit virus software.
Bussiness data will be backed up periodically to ensure safty of data using increamental back up strategy.
Role based security will be applied for Application data and operations accessibility.
